⚡️ Ethereum Foundation cuts costs to boost DeFi

The Ethereum Foundation has introduced a new treasury policy aimed at strengthening the decentralization and resilience of the network.

✅ Over the next five years, the foundation plans to reduce its operating expenses to 5%, following an endowment-style model.

The Ethereum Foundation is betting on DeFi tools, including staking and lending, with a focus on security and rejection of centralized solutions.
